@page "/"

<PageTitle>CarbonBlazor template</PageTitle>

<CbBreadcrumb>
    <CbBreadcrumbItem Current="true">Overview</CbBreadcrumbItem>
</CbBreadcrumb>

<section class="docs-hero">
    <h1>Carbon-inspired Blazor WebAssembly template</h1>
    <p>Reusable Blazor components, runtime theme tokens, accessible interaction patterns, and a documentation app for building product interfaces with Carbon-like logic.</p>
    <CbButtonSet>
        <CbButton>Browse components</CbButton>
        <CbButton Variant="CbButtonVariant.Secondary">View foundations</CbButton>
    </CbButtonSet>
</section>

<section class="docs-grid">
    <CbTile>
        <h2>Reusable library</h2>
        <p>The CarbonBlazor Razor Class Library owns component APIs, CSS tokens, and JS interop helpers.</p>
    </CbTile>
    <CbTile>
        <h2>Runtime theming</h2>
        <p>White, Gray 10, Gray 90, and Gray 100 themes are applied with CbThemeProvider and CSS custom properties.</p>
    </CbTile>
    <CbTile>
        <h2>Accessible interactions</h2>
        <p>Components expose roles, keyboard behavior, focus states, and bindable Blazor parameters.</p>
    </CbTile>
</section>
